{"tid":799969,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部：聯合航空再怎麼想有「彈性」 都跳不出一個中國的原則","createTime":"2018-08-30T13:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T16:56:48.000Z","uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d39969e1925a0a63e446d09ef0828be876e756a2","tid":799969,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T13:17:43.000Z","msg":"美航空公司以貨幣區分兩岸三地　外交部：一中原則不變<br />\n2018-08-30 HKT 17:29<br />\n<br />\n有美國航空公司網站以貨幣區分中國大陸、台灣及香港。外交部發言人華春瑩表示，有關人士再怎麼想有「彈性」，都跳不出「一個中國」的根本原則和遵循。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩說，航空公司網站涉及台灣名稱問題，由中國民航部門負責處理，她強調，世界上只有一個中國，台灣是中國一部分，這是客觀事實、基本常識和國際共識，亦是任何外國公司在華經營的基本遵循。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1415387-20180830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1415387-20180830.htm&d=CWckCpRgw86jkyshiiOlsOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=916a5762\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1415387-20180830.htm&h=4501b0a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1415387-20180830.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d7fd4c8a045b443585e2270a0fe45d190440048e","tid":799969,"uid":95,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T13:20:24.000Z","msg":"傻鳩根本無人會當台灣係中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db2af1ce687c68eaf47b8d0cb9dcb099f33e080a","tid":799969,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T13:30:25.000Z","msg":"人唔笑狗都吠"},{"pid":"5b25f706a1b47d2876c64b91fb860227e53b2791","tid":799969,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T13:31:07.000Z","msg":"之後可以點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟本啲說話係俾返強國人用嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794a55c98f2162445403917101255141c1dff371","tid":7999